{"tid":595091,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"雲南武術隊表演套路 老前輩暈倒體育館不治","createTime":"2018-03-16T11:25:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-16T11:25:04.000Z","uid":41404,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9c0f92026851d2e1c6de400489fbf6dd0b110429","tid":595091,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T11:25:04.000Z","msg":"雲南武術套路隊早前來港，今午4時許在馬鞍山體育館進行表演活動，惟當表演完畢，武術隊準備離開時，隊中一名老前輩突然暈倒，送院搶救後證實不治。警方調查後，相信事件並無可疑。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180316/57956519\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180316%2F57956519&d=mtiUfB9ZA3VS0CGbD5Rfyozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=8052fa70\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180316%2F57956519&h=a7ccd98b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180316/57956519</a>"}]}